main

public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
Main method of Yeti. Arguments are numerous. Here is a list of the current ones: -java : for calling it on Java -timeout=X : for calling Yeti for a given amount of time (X can be minutes or seconds, e.g. 2mn | 3s ) -nTest : for calling Yeti to attempt that many method calls -testModules=M1:M2:...:Mn : for testing one or several modules

Parameters:
args - the arguments of the program
